profile:
At Call The Mover LTD we understand that for many people, relocating is one of the most stressful things they have to do. Our team of experienced movers are trained to ease that stress and complete your move hassle free. Our professional staff will ensure that your possessions arrive safely at your destination and that you pay a great price for a great service.

We specialize in packing and moving services for both residential and commercial clients. We also offer a sling shot pick up & delivery service. 


Contact Call the Mover LTD at our Calgary or Chestermere office and let us handle your next move. Enjoy the peace of mind that our regular clients experience that comes with knowing your possessions are in the capable hands of a skilled, dedicated, licensed and insured team.
services: Moving and packing, Sling shot deliveries, equipment hauling
